IN THE COURT OF THE {{COURT_NAME}}
AT {{COURT_PLACE}}

O.S. No. {{SUIT_NUMBER}} / {{SUIT_YEAR}}

The Plaintiff, {{PLAINTIFF_NAME}}, on filing this suit before the District Court at {{DISTRICT_NAME}} on {{FILING_DATE}}, seeks partition and separate possession of the ancestral property described in Schedule of Property (Annexure II) situated at {{PROPERTY_LOCATION}}, with the genealogical ties set out in Annexure I, and to the extent of Plaintiff’s 1/3rd share as evidenced by the family lineage in Annexure I, and prays for the following: 

(a) A preliminary decree declaring that the Plaintiff is entitled to a 1/3rd undivided share in the ancestral property described in Schedule of Property (Annexure II) and that the Defendant’s rights be adjusted as per partition, and directing that the said property be partitioned and that a Commissioner be appointed to effect partition, frame a plan showing allotment of the Plaintiff’s 1/3rd share to Plaintiff and to deliver possession accordingly, in accordance with the genealogical table attached at Annexure I; 

(b) A final decree for partition and separate possession in terms of the preliminary decree, allotting to the Plaintiff his 1/3rd share by physical partition or by allotment of specific portions in Schedule of Property as per the plan prepared and certified by the Commissioner, with delivery of vacant possession to the Plaintiff and with conveyance of title to the portion allotted to Plaintiff; 

(c) Appointment of a Commissioner to execute the partition, prepare a partition plan, determine possession and possession dates, and file a report with a schedule of parcels and a map within six months from the date of the order, with liberty to make such modifications as may be directed by the Court; 

(d) Costs of the suit, including costs of this partition proceedings and the Commissioner’s fees, in terms of Rs. {{COSTS_AMOUNT}} and other allowable costs, to be paid by the Defendant to the Plaintiff; 

(e) Any other relief the Court deems fit.
Annexure I: Genealogy Table; Annexure II: Schedule of Property.

Any other relief the Court deems fit.

